{"tid":2423084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇一個人可以蠢過中大校長段狗？","createTime":"2021-02-25T16:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T06:20:47.000Z","uid":82640,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"42cda6807c1ac6270769701d0260b1c4f97edc03","tid":2423084,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"你乜柒都唔做俾建制狗搞到過唔到撥款<br />\n = 建制派阻香港創科發展<br />\n = 打爛人飯碗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大咁多宣傳人才咁多人脈<br />\n洗撚睇嗰啲西環門口狗面色咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n段狗你咁割蓆完建制派都唔會滿意㗎啦<br />\n會滿意你使撚撤回？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建制派自從泛民總辭後無嘢做搵嘢嚟攻擊<br />\n佢哋一直就業不足就會搵嘢出嚟挑剔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全係今日割一城明日割十城啲friend<br />\n段狗打後繼續兩邊不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n段狗個心態好似毒撚追女仔咁<br />\n比得上1st hon結扎條柒頭<br />\n佢成件事最多高調咁做返受害者扮無奈就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身可以明明乜都唔使做<br />\n硬係要伸個頭出嚟做多咗<br />\n冇撚腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大校長係比較難做<br />\n但9大入面段狗一定係最蠢嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336bb12219e203d5bba429a2b2b238ce12b7c692","tid":2423084,"uid":221171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P2nDXWC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP2nDXWC.jpg&h=a980dd57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSzZHoh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSzZHoh.jpg&h=a9f9df22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58cb0327a014fc71aaa3d77a40a0a0e3648651b3","tid":2423084,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"336bb12219e203d5bba429a2b2b238ce12b7c692","tid":2423084,"uid":221171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1